Gardevoir (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0281: Kirlia
Pokémon
#0283: Surskit →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Gardevoir (TCG Pocket).

Gardevoir has been featured on 27 different cards since it debuted in the EX Ruby & Sapphire expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Gardevoir cards are normally Psychic-type Stage 2 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Gardevoir

Gardevoir
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
